      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? I\u2019ve taken such good care of this beauty, and it\u2019s in absolutely pristine, mint condition. From the spotless interior to the gleaming paint, it\u2019s basically perfect. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019ll make someone very happy! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
