    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Offering a pristine AP2-generation S2000, a masterclass in atmospheric engineering. At its heart lies the F22C1 2.2L DOHC VTEC power plant, delivering a linear power band and an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain features a triple-cone synchronized 6-speed close-ratio gearbox paired with a Torsen limited-slip differential for optimal torque biasing. The chassis is a rigid X-bone frame supported by an unmolested four-wheel double-wishbone suspension, ensuring surgical handling. Every bushing, seal, and mechanical interface remains in factory-fresh condition, offering a visceral, analog driving experience that is increasingly rare.",
      "price": 48500.0,
