    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously maintained to the highest standard. This car looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero paint chips, swirl marks, or scratches, recently treated with a professional-grade ceramic coating for long-term protection. Inside, the cabin is pristine\u2014the premium leather is supple with no creasing or wear on the bolsters, and the original protective films remain on several interior trim pieces. Mechanically, it is flawless; every service has been performed ahead of schedule at the authorized dealership, with a full portfolio of records included. The engine bay is spotless, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road wear or oxidation. This is a single-owner, non-smoker vehicle that has been stored in a climate-controlled garage since day one. It comes with two sets of keys, the original window sticker, and all owner manuals. If you are looking for the absolute best example of this model available on the market today, this is it.",
      "price": 44900.0,
